My Morning Checklist
====================

Sweep
-----

[ ] Put phone away
[ ] Journal log entry (get up time, current status, goals for the day)
[ ] Check calendar, anything to keep track of?
[ ] Process personal email inbox (remember 2-minute rule)
[ ] Process work email inbox (remember 2-minute rule)
[ ] Process Slack notifications

Process
-------

[ ] Process Evernote inbox (top to bottom)
[ ] Clear Evernote waiting list

Start
-----

[ ] Switch to Work Hot notebook
[ ] If no items in Work Hot, go move some inbox items
[ ] Pick one and start working!
